 class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔會點會咁多攻略 改檔<br />\n邊個玩中國版 到依家仲係得Mario cart <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee58fb2a60edb4fe02a88902ccd63484abfb06d0","tid":2064591,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T03:03:04.000Z","msg":"任天堂啲創作自由度勁高<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等我去splatoon 寫個8964 天滅中共"},{"pid":"30a4aa4670901c230484fc6f188c0f42febc036a","tid":2064591,"uid":249160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T03:03:53.000Z","msg":"冇野好玩了 玩返俄羅斯方塊算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/dog.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d5df09b9af94d867d2fbcfc1367c7b707d246f0","tid":2064591,"uid":132729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a3388d27e083c0302182636291ed0b89649b4837","tid":2064591,"uid":204539,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T03:00:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「<strong>猛男撿樹枝</strong>」</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T03:11:28.000Z","msg":"諗起早兩年biohazard改名到我到警局上班的第一天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50baa8c5a8ea990cb0d3356137ad1bc88dd9abe","tid":2064591,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T03:12:11.000Z","msg":"就快呼吸也是「辱華」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddb9c61dd7f3f9eb265e16995f82b824f3e5657d","tid":2064591,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T03:12:40.000Z","msg":"所以「支那」是「辱華」, 係好可疑既說法！"},{"pid":"a2241a4c25644f7080e0cad2ef1ffc5ff1a43f9d","tid":2064591,"uid":162095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T03:18:53.000Z","msg":"得啦得啦，好悶啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\